Sumedh S. Thakar 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Product Officer at QUALYS INC, Sumedh S. Thakar  made $3,361,418 in total compensation.  Of this total $308,718 was received as a salary, $94,896 was received as a bonus, $1,433,318 was received in stock options, $1,519,542 was awarded as stock and $4,944 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


